Section 2 (The Shifting Maze - The Puzzle): The Callback. The path twists. The players must use the Rule of Disturbance (from Thornheart Grove) to navigate. When they take an action, the map rotates 90 degrees.
Section 3 (The Roots - The Setback): The roots of the Eldergleam attack. Spriggans ambush from the walls.
Section 4 (The Sanctuary - The Boss Fight): Gaelen is on the high ground, raining fire. He summons Ascended Sleepers.
The Escape Condition: If defeated or if the ritual succeeds, Gaelen does not flee on foot. He AscendsΓÇöteleporting away in a column of fire (Divine Intervention style), viewing this as moving to the next "garden."


Section 5 (The Sapling): The reward/restoration scene.

Adventure C: The Captives of Ansilvund (Stony Creek)
Villain: Antoine of Forelhost (Controller/Alchemist - Dragon Cult).
