The Dead Man's Switch: The captives are rigged to die if Antoine's heart stops (or he manually triggers it).
The Decoy: He may use a body double or illusion.
The Escape: Antoine has multiple exit strategies (Invisibility, Vent System, Surrender/Betrayal). It is almost certain he will escape to aid Rahgot later.




Section 5 (The Vault): Where the "Scourge" formula is kept (if he left it) and the surviving prisoners are freed.

